OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FClimate claims on household
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbasics investigated        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "Green" claims made in advertising for 
OL,6, household basics, such as washing-up   
OL,7, liquid, are to be scrutinised to see if
OL,8, they are misleading.                   
OL,10,FThe Competition and Markets Authority  
OL,11,F(CMA) says it is concerned consumers   
OL,12,Fare "paying a premium for products that
OL,13,Faren't what they seem".                
OL,15,FIt will examine the accuracy of        
OL,16,Fenvironmental claims on goods such as  
OL,17,Fcleaning products and toiletries.      
OL,19,FCMA boss Sarah Cardell says she is     
OL,20,Fconcerned companies are "greenwashing".
